OL,6,FHe said the nationality of one of the
OL,7,Fdead couldn't be immediately verified,
OL,8,Fwhile another person was still
OL,9,Funaccounted for.
OL,11,FEight people were also injured, with
OL,12,Ftwo in a serious condition.
OL,14,FIn the past few decades, many people
OL,15,Ffrom China, including ethnic Koreans,
OL,16,Fhave migrated to South Korea to seek
OL,17,Fjobs.
