OL,4,C22 in South Korea
OL,6,FLike other foreign migrants from
OL,7,FSoutheast Asian nations, they often
OL,8,Fend up in factories or in physically
OL,9,Fdemanding and low-paying jobs shunned
OL,10,Fby more affluent South Koreans.
OL,12,FThe fire started at one of the factory
OL,13,Fbuildings owned by a company named
OL,14,FAricell.
OL,16,FKim said that authorities will
OL,17,Finvestigate whether there were fire
OL,18,Fextinguishing systems at the site and
OL,19,Fif they worked.
