OL,6,FKim said a total of 102 people were
OL,7,Fworking at the factory when the fire
OL,8,Fbroke out.
OL,10,FPrime minister Han Duck-soo and
OL,11,Finterior and safety minister Lee Sang-
OL,12,Fmin visited the site later on Monday.
OL,14,FHan asked officials to provide
OL,15,Fgovernment assistance for funeral
OL,16,Fservices and support programmes for
OL,17,Fvictims' relatives, according to Han's
OL,18,Foffice.
